{"tid":1729400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過對家係用支所謂音波炮等我哋恐慌，可能只係靠嚇","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T08:13:47.000Z","uid":340106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eacd79cdf2ba1a95fda14be70d6985b7e9cc79e6","tid":1729400,"uid":340106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"首先你要搞清聲波攻擊嘅種類:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">超聲波</span>:&gt;20000Hz聽唔到，喺空氣係高衰減率，同埋難繞射，即係一定要對準人嚟射先有大效<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">次聲波</span>:&lt;20Hz聽唔到，喺空氣衰減低即係可以傳得遠啲，繞射能力強，即係揾啲吸音差嘅物料擋係冇用，兼且通常要喺空曠地方用否則會反射向自己(喺軍事用途上音波源附近通常唔會放兵)<br />\n<br />\n仲有我見有人問聲波會唔會干擾通訊，大佬呀通訊係用電磁波㗎，聲音係機械波，兩樣野完全獨立㗎。<br />\n耳機耳塞有冇用？有，因為耳仔係最食聲，但軍司用嘅聲波攻擊係針對全身，目的係震傷器官eg腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">結論</span>:黑警有可能只係虛張聲勢，引人係喺連登洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。有錯有漏歡迎糾正"},{"pid":"babda7338c016ed11be51c60db0a3c9b6c1216c3","tid":1729400,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"警察砲轟poly，要推畀國際知！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 組不斷更新 Task3</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=fd2ef855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">/task3</span></span>就得！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一定要響外國議員/名人/外媒關於香港的tweets reply Poly最新情況，向國際求救</span><br />\n<br />\n！！！眾志：解放軍拎自動步槍同刺刀<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1195948090118721536?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1195948090118721536%3Fs%3D19&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ4ICM%2BRBTk%2By